flowchart LR
  CC[Clinical Conversation] --> LV[Live Voice Capture]
  LV --> AI[AI Triage Engine\nSemantic Kernel]
  AI --> RC{Risk + Confidence Check}

  RC -->|Routine case| NX[Auto-route Next Step]
  RC -->|Complex or high-risk case| HR[Human Review]
  HR --> AP[Clinician Approval]
  AP --> NX

  NX --> RU[Records Updated]
  NX --> FS[Follow-up Scheduled]
  NX --> PN[Patient Notification]

  RU --> OUT[Operational Time Saved\nFaster, safer care coordination]
  FS --> OUT
  PN --> OUT

  STK[Powered by\nReact micro frontends + .NET 9 microservices + Dapr]:::stack

